Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要介紹一位氣象播報小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.66,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過尋呼機推理也能讓心境撥雲見日哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.68,0:00:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.97,0:00:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣預報小姐綁架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨 快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.72,0:01:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾 毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個差一點就被淋成四隻落湯雞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午會下雷雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個天氣預報的姐姐說得還真準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.87,0:02:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.46,0:02:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出去工作必須在那裡過夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答錄機裡面有留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.88,0:02:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要隨便亂碰哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.97,0:02:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我在日賣電視臺工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫淺野亞紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.34,0:02:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是因為有點急事想跟毛利先生談談才打電話來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然您不在家的話 那我再打電話來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺野亞紀是什麼人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.91,0:02:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播報天氣的那個姐姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她都在日賣電視臺播報天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.69,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個大姐姐也有在《新聞城市》裡出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是她的忠實粉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.06,0:02:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說有急事要找毛利叔叔會是什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 這次就換我們這少年偵探團去拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.22,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個播報天氣的大姐姐有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日賣電視臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.86,0:03:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 原來你們就是代替毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地到這裡來找我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.41,0:03:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果碰到什麼麻煩事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.81,0:03:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就告訴我們少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們去查就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.99,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 今天負責接待小朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津久茂小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.10,0:03:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了討人喜歡 不得不和這些小鬼打交道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招牌播報員還真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化妝真是有夠誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那指甲是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我沒有這麼想過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可都要乖乖的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別給這位大姐姐的工作添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人看了就覺得討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.08,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是在亞紀姐姐之前就在《新聞城市》播報的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.02,0:03:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是在半年以前才換到這個工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說妳想跟毛利叔叔商量的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道跟這個津久茂小姐有關嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想知道名偵探毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願不願意上我們《新聞城市》這個節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真沒意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼事件就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.25,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事       什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的尋呼機啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.03,0:04:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常一下子就會跑得不見人影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帶在身上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.16,0:04:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你自己不是也有行動電話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 是接收器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已經壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 都是為了正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面留的是偵探事務所的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是小蘭姐姐打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個尋呼機的號碼能不能告訴我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.69,0:04:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有事要拜託少年偵探團的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就跟你們聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.49,0:04:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.28,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就有了少年偵探團的號碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我已經記下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是專門用來顯示數字的機子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是用這種的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還會把數字組合成好多種訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟自己的朋友打著玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這種機子只能顯示數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們把它看成英文字母以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合數字就可以顯示不同的留言內容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好比說打上428代表的就是涉谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,428
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しぶや
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 既然大家好不容易來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.16,0:05:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不想到《新聞城市》的攝影棚裡去看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.18,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是淺野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.36,0:05:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.89,0:05:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.95,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.07,0:06:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐突然有個工作要處理 所以必須立刻趕過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.92,0:06:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.20,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.21,0:06:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請你幫我帶這幾個孩子到攝影棚那裡去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在突然有個工作要處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.38,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有通行證也麻煩你辦一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家就跟我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐到底要我們等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 突然找妳來帶班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒沒什麼 聽說亞紀她被人恐嚇了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.24,0:06:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在我會分心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.98,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是被人恐嚇了就嚇得逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀根本就沒有資格做新聞人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要開始拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.57,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美小姐她一向不喜歡小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說亞紀姐姐被人恐嚇了是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.91,0:07:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是代替偵探毛利先生來這裡見她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那個名偵探嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.15,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.02,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.41,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是從亞紀小姐追蹤報導一個政治家瀆職的事情之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才開始接到一些恐嚇她終止採訪的信件和電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天她就接到一封如果她上《新聞城市》報導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要殺了她的恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道亞紀小姐要跟叔叔談的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這封恐嚇信件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《新聞城市》的拍攝狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從這個電視上看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.75,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 叔叔還有其他工作要做 待會見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.73,0:07:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候打到亞紀姐姐行動電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會就是那通恐嚇電話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐她因為害怕而...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐才不是那種膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你也這麼認為吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得亞紀小姐在用行動電話跟人交談的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有一點害怕的神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.89,0:08:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那個樣子還好像是接到一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別報導的案子特別開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個絕對不可能是恐嚇電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是引誘亞紀小姐出去的陷阱的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是小蘭姐姐打的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.22,0:08:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是亞紀姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為知道這個尋呼機號碼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.55,0:08:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有小蘭姐姐和亞紀姐姐兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.53,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.03,0:08:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是淺野亞紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有點事外出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的人請您留…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你為什麼掛斷電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是亞紀姐姐打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是亞紀姐姐家沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 是電話答錄機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她既然不在為什麼會留家裡的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,110
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.71,0:09:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是110啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是110不是警察局的電話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察怎麼會打電話給我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 是亞紀姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐現在一定被壞人抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才想要我們幫她通知警方知道這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣她自己也可以跟警方聯絡的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她現在根本沒有辦法說話的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.23,0:09:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.58,0:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9109
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是亞紀姐姐家電話號碼的區號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果光靠這些留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.79,0:09:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的向警方報案他們也不會受理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果警方不受理的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們少年偵探團出面的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只靠這些訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能知道亞紀姐姐在哪裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.84,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.94,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著為您播報體壇的體育新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在國立競技場裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所舉行的日本聯盟東京Spirits…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是亞紀姐姐報得比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2003
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個號碼應該念成仁王樣(におうさま)才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以亞紀姐姐一定在有仁王像的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能推理得像樣一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7點20分以後收到的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼意思根本就搞不清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在為您播報最新收到的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次因為沿海開發引起的瀆職案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京地檢署特搜部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已經約談政治家丸谷先生與大久保先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.29,0:11:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對多起賄賂案件到案說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.96,0:11:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道亞紀姐姐這些資訊的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這些資訊表示的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這些接受了賄賂的政客的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.03,0:11:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0就代表丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是丸谷的第一個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00就是大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是大久保的第一個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於096的96就是黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說丸谷很黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.36,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐要傳達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.76,0:11:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指出接受賄賂的這個姓丸谷的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.76,0:11:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那2003和5656的意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.62,0:12:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在銀行那裡接受賄賂的帳號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.35,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 我想亞紀姐姐現在一定被關在丸谷家才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕快去救她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個丸谷住的地方就在西帝丹鎮那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從這裡坐地下鐵只要一站就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一直在打雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.85,0:12:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.93,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看著別讓人靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你快點上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.69,0:12:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個在搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快給我下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.70,0:12:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們竟然丟下我自己跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次如果再去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要想辦法對付那些狗和那個警衛才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛明明就是你第一個跑掉的 你還敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.82,0:13:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.91,0:13:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.96,0:13:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.42,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又下起雨來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小蘭姐姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了你還在什麼地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚的時候我有Call你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒有回我對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我馬上就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在快給我回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們那裡現在正在打雷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雷聲而且雨也下的好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這邊天氣很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮也好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們這裡正在下大雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我暫時回不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你現在到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我拿雨傘去接你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.51,0:14:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.82,0:14:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.06,0:14:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著預報明天的天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關東東部明天天氣晴朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過北部卻是陰雨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.43,0:14:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南部地區明天應該會是晴天才對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點回電視臺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.84,0:14:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先解釋一下嘛 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看喔 你們把2003立起來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立起來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.48,0:15:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文的MOON也就是月亮的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.27,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.77,0:15:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐在一開始之所以給我們打2003的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的就是要我們抬頭看看月亮的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她傳2003這個訊息的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在晚上7點20分對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.42,0:15:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候月亮應該在天空的東南方才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是丸谷先生家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東南方那個方位蓋了一棟大廈根本看不到月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.58,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐不會在那個丸谷的家裡對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐現在應該是被關在一個看得到月亮的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是光靠月亮我們根本不知道在哪裡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.64,0:15:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以亞紀姐姐才會利用數字來表示當時的天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己所在的地點每個時間的天氣變化顯示給我們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0就是圓圈 也就是陰轉晴的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00就表示兩個圓圈 所以就是陰天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於096就是(丸に黒)兩個圓圈全部塗黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是雨天的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.21,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她在8點31分的時候傳的5656呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.12,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用聲音來表示打雷的話會是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟隆 轟隆 (ゴロゴロ)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 5656代表的就是打雷的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.43,0:16:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說在晚上8點30分的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是下雨又有打雷的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.57,0:16:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是亞紀姐姐被關著的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上8點半左右的時候有雷雨的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以我們電視臺為中心半徑大概有一公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直徑大概兩公里的範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.88,0:16:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還下一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.18,0:16:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南想得果然沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說亞紀姐姐應該就在附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0109 是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,01代表的不就是晴天的記號嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這一帶天上都還有烏雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定還有別的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想0109代表的一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗的鰻魚便當才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐現在一定是餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是你自己餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在好餓哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我餓了有那麼好笑嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 對不起 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在笑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次多虧有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會知道亞紀姐姐在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型道具的倉庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟姐姐在那裡走散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個倉庫應該是在一樓最北邊的房間才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.09,0:18:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.49,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐在大型道具間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的0109就像元太所說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要把它分成0、10和9來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 10 9
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,お とう く
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型道具 (おおどうぐ)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.02,0:18:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視臺的出口本來就不多可是房間很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.38,0:18:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果歹徒也是內部人的話就只有用這個方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你已經知道歹徒到底是什麼人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.49,0:18:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐已經用尋呼機告訴我歹徒是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想逃也是逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖的束手就擒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先用電話把亞紀姐姐叫出去之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用事先準備的藥物讓她睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把她關在最裡面的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家以為亞紀姐姐是因為害怕那封恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才放下工作匆匆逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是利用了亞紀姐姐對你的信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把她從《新聞城市》這個節目趕出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是亞紀姐姐卻從窗戶看到外面天空的變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用她的行動電話將天空的變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個一個傳到我尋呼機上讓我們知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是亞紀姐姐傳給我的這些訊息裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個我剛才一直解不開的就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9109
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.12,0:19:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個號碼是我們在收到110像報警訊息之後收到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.24,0:19:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個既不是指示亞紀姐姐所在位置的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.26,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒的名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.78,0:19:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想從我們少年偵探的手中逃走再等一百年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.70,0:20:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐 醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.71,0:20:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞紀姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9109
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以分解成9、10還有9
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一個一個換成漢字以後念的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.96,0:20:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津久茂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.84,0:20:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津久茂小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.00,0:20:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是太恨亞紀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我才是《新聞城市》的元老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個節目先是由我播報的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.15,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.99,0:20:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就看著她比我長得年輕貌美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就把我換下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.04,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此妳就應該靠實力再搶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管妳有什麼理由都沒有辦法讓它名正言順的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.13,0:22:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是今天白天的氣象報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.76,0:22:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.15,0:22:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事真是謝謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.53,0:22:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.39,0:23:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能看出我的訊息表示的是天氣的記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不愧是少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.73,0:23:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.61,0:23:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.68,0:23:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼知道那個歹徒就是津久茂小姐的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.93,0:23:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被蒙住鼻子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.39,0:23:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實已經看到歹徒的指甲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.22,0:23:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.47,0:23:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指甲彩繪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.61,0:23:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.58,0:23:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她在指甲上做的彩繪指甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.63,0:23:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟天氣圖實在是有點相像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.85,0:23:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才記住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說元太你就代表霰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.98,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.63,0:23:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.73,0:23:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.64,0:23:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有點像耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.92,0:23:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你代表的還不只霰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.33,0:23:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰雹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.27,0:23:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這些是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.56,0:23:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間貼滿偶像的海報耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是寫真集還是CD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.64,0:24:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都有兩份耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.85,0:24:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.09,0:24:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還有她們各自的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.62,0:24:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.60,0:24:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是他殺
